{"word":"G2903 - κράτιστος - krátistos - krat'-is-tos - Most excellent","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κράτιστος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">krátistos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">krat'-is-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Most excellent</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"கனம் பொருந்திய - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"mightiest, strongest, noblest, most illustrious, best, most excellent"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Superlative of a derivative of <a href=\"#/G2904 - κράτος - krátos - krat'-os/2904\">G2904</a>; <i>strongest</i>, that is, (in dignity) <i>very honorable:</i> - most excellent (noble).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2888/2888\">G2888</a>, <a href=\"#/G2900/2900\">G2900</a>, <a href=\"#/G2901/2901\">G2901</a>, <a href=\"#/G2902/2902\">G2902</a>, <a href=\"#/G2903/2903\">G2903</a>, <a href=\"#/G2904/2904\">G2904</a>, <a href=\"#/G3841/3841\">G3841</a>"}]}